            "task_description": "<div class=\"collapsible collapsible--text\">\n<p>Each team is required to prepare a credit rating report on an ASX-listed company. Students will conduct a comprehensive credit risk analysis and assign a credit rating to the selected company. In preparing the report, students can draw on the credit rating methodologies used by major rating agencies.</p>\n<p>Team reports must be submitted by the deadline specified above.</p>\n<p>More detailed instructions will be provided on Blackboard.</p>\n<p>A peer review process will be used to provide feedback on individual contributions to the team assessment. Students must complete the peer review to receive their final mark for this assessment item.</p>\n<p>The results of the peer review may be used to adjust an individual student’s overall score for this assessment item, based on their peer-reviewed contribution and performance.</p>\n<p>Further information about the peer review process is provided in the Assessment Guideline on Blackboard.</p>\n<button class=\"collapsible__toggle\">\n<span class=\"collapsible__open link--icon icon--standard--arrow-down-1\">Read full task description</span>\n<span class=\"collapsible__close link--icon icon--standard--arrow-up-1\">Hide full task description</span>\n</button>\n</div>",
